data.description: Welcome Home to this ADORABLE bungalow in the heart of Battle Creek.  You will absolutely love the character displayed through the original hardwood floors and arched doorways.  The  main floor features a nice sized living room, a cozy dining area open to the kitchen, two good sized rooms, and an updated bathroom.  Upstairs, you will fall in LOVE with the massive primary room complete with a sitting area/office area and walk in closet.  The basement surprises with space for entertainment/play and storage/laundry.  All of this just minutes from KCC.  Schedule your private showing today!
